title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Vapid FMJ MK V Now Widely Available
content:
The FMJ MK V was originally meant to be a track-only prototype paying homage to a late 1960s Vapid legend. Like all great technical innovations, the MK V somehow found its way into production, onto civilian streets, and into racing lore almost instantly.

The Vapid FMJ MK V (Super) is now available for general purchase at Legendary Motorsport or the Luxury Autos showroom.
